P509.label: cause of death

P1196.label: manner of death
P1196.description: circumstances of a person's death; one of: natural causes, accident, suicide, homicide, pending investigation or special 'unknown value'.  Use 'cause of death' (P509) for more immediate or underlying causes and events, e.g. heart attack, car accident
P1196.suggestedValuesText: one of: natural causes (Q3739104), accident (Q171558), suicide (Q10737), homicide (Q149086), pending investigation (Q15729048), capital punishment (Q8454) or the special 'unknown value'. Do not expand list of allowed values. This property is tied to the US Standard Death Certificate.
